@node "install_alockutils" "ALockUtils-Install"


                           ALockUtils Version 1.1

                   Installation (ALockUtils installation)


 The easiest way to install ALockUtils is to use installation script. Just
 double-click "ALockUtils-Install" icon and installer will do the rest.

 Installer utility is required.
 
 @{" Manual installation    " link "install_alockutils_manually" 0}
@endnode

@node "install_alock" "ALock-Install"

                           ALockUtils Version 1.1

                     Installation  (ALock installation)


 Original ALock package does not include installer script. The installation
 of ALock is quite easy, but I made installer script anyway.

 Unpack ALock archive somewhere and drag "ALock-Install"-icon to the same
 directory. Double-click "ALock-Install"-icon and installer will do the rest.

 Installer utility and ALock package are required.
@endnode

