                  |   @{"@| Enabled " link "" 0} Mailbox check         |
                  |                                      |
                  |   @{"@| Enabled " link "" 0} Show MOTD             |
                  |                                      |
                  |   @{"@| Enabled " link "" 0} Show Individual MOTD  |
                  |                                      |
